      <title>特朗普威胁丹麦因格陵兰征收关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-07/trump-threatens-denmark-with-tariffs-over-greenland-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普拒绝排除对巴拿马运河和格陵兰岛采取经济和军事手段的可能性，并表示可能对丹麦征收“极高”关税。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-07/trump-threatens-denmark-with-tariffs-over-greenland-video</guid>
