    <item>
      <title>雷德伯恩看好流媒体业务前景，迪士尼股价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/disney-shares-gain-as-redburn-turns-bullish-on-streaming-outlook</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位已成为这家媒体巨头最大看涨者的分析师表示，华特迪士尼公司 (Walt Disney Co.) 的流媒体服务已达到可以超越其陷入困境的电视服务的水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/disney-shares-gain-as-redburn-turns-bullish-on-streaming-outlook</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 17:20:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据消息人士称，泰晤士水务公司将于下个月向投资者寻求新的投标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/thames-water-said-to-seek-new-bids-from-investors-by-next-month</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，泰晤士水务公司的潜在投资者必须在 2 月 10 日之前提交对该水务公司的新投标，因为这家陷入困境的公司正在紧急注入股权以增强其财务状况。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/thames-water-said-to-seek-new-bids-from-investors-by-next-month</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 17:19:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>西班牙 HBX 集团计划最早于下周启动 IPO</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/spain-s-hbx-group-said-to-plan-ipo-kickoff-as-soon-as-next-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，西班牙旅游科技公司 HBX 集团正考虑最早于下周宣布首次公开募股计划，这可能是 2025 年欧洲首批大型上市之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/spain-s-hbx-group-said-to-plan-ipo-kickoff-as-soon-as-next-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 17:11:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>债券市场火爆销售，吸引追求收益的买家</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/frenzy-of-sales-in-red-hot-debt-market-draws-yield-hungry-buyers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[借款人正以前所未有的速度涌入全球债务市场，试图利用渴望信贷的管理者的需求。这些管理者资金充裕，已经导致公司债券利差降至近 30 年来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/frenzy-of-sales-in-red-hot-debt-market-draws-yield-hungry-buyers</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 16:37:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛的哈祖斯表示，如果没有关税，通胀率将下降得更快</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-07/goldman-s-hatzius-expect-three-rate-cuts-this-year-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛首席经济学家 Jan Hatzius 表示，如果当选总统唐纳德·特朗普不对所有进口产品征收关税，通胀将会更快下降。特朗普承诺对所有进口商品征收 10% 至 20% 的全面关税。Hatzius 还表示，他预计美联储今年将降息三次。

（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-07/goldman-s-hatzius-expect-three-rate-cuts-this-year-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 16:33:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞士再保险穆勒：欧洲经济增长分化将继续</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-07/europe-growth-divergence-to-continue-swiss-re-s-mueller-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士再保险欧洲首席经济学家夏洛特·穆勒认为欧洲的增长分化将继续，并表示欧洲和中国将受到全球贸易不确定性的拖累，而美国将成为主要的表现者。她在“彭博日报欧洲版”节目中与汤姆·麦肯齐进行了交谈。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-07/europe-growth-divergence-to-continue-swiss-re-s-mueller-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 16:32:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根大通三名银行高管跳槽至三井住友银行后重组 CLO 集团</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/jpmorgan-shakes-up-clo-group-after-banking-trio-left-for-smbc</link>
      <description><![CDATA[不到三个月前，摩根大通的三位资深银行家跳槽至三井住友金融集团的竞争对手平台，此后，该行正在对其抵押贷款债务业务的领导层进行改组。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/jpmorgan-shakes-up-clo-group-after-banking-trio-left-for-smbc</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 16:26:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧元区通胀数据回升，欧洲股市上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/european-stocks-dip-as-tech-gains-fade-focus-shifts-to-cpi-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于欧元区 12 月份通胀数据上升，欧洲股市周二上涨，支持欧洲央行逐步降息的理由，但不会阻止其降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/european-stocks-dip-as-tech-gains-fade-focus-shifts-to-cpi-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 08:18:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
